Class ResourceList

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
java.util.AbstractList<E>
java.util.ArrayList<Resource>
com.telenav.kivakit.resource.ResourceList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Resource>, Collection<Resource>, List<Resource>, RandomAccess
public class ResourceList extends ArrayList<Resource>
A list of Resources. Adds the methods:
  • largest() - The largest resource in this list
  • matching(Extension) - All resources with the given extension
  • matching(Matcher) - All matching resources
  • smallest() - The smallest resource in this list
  • totalSize() - The total size of the resources in this list
